text: Artur Kuznetsov (; born 9 March 1995) is a Ukrainian football defender. He plays for Ukrainian side Metalurh Zaporizhya. ==Career== Kuznetsov is a product of youth team system FC Metalurh Zaporizhya. His first trainer was Oleksandr Rudyka. He made his debut for FC Metalurh in the main-squad playing against FC Dnipro Dnipropetrovsk on 15 March 2015 in the Ukrainian Premier League. In January 2016, he signed a contract with another Ukrainian Premier League side FC Chornomorets Odesa. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at FFU Official Site (Ukr) * Category:1995 births Category:FC Chornomorets Odesa players Category:FC Metalurh Zaporizhya players Category:Living people Category:Ukraine youth international footballers Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Ukrainian Premier League players Category:Association football defenders
